comments: Durant (BKN) and Powell (DAL) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Claxton (BKN) brings his hand forward towards Doncic's (DAL) front and marginal contact occurs during the drive.
Doncic (DAL) momentarily brings his off-arm under Claxton's (BKN) right arm, and marginal contact occurs at the start of the drive.
Claxton (BKN) cleanly dislodges the ball from Doncic (DAL).  Any ensuing arm contact after the dislodge is considered marginal.
Harris (BKN) and Green (DAL) briefly come together off-ball, and incidental leg-to-leg contact occurs.
Finney-Smith (DAL) brings his hands towards Durant (BKN) and marginal contact occurs as he releases from the contact.
Durant (BKN) is already in Green's (DAL) path and is firming up when marginal contact occurs as the defenders switch.
Powell (DAL) exits the paint within three seconds.
Doncic (DAL) steps slightly forward towards Thomas (BKN) and marginal contact occurs on the perimeter.
Harris (BKN) is moving alongside Doncic's (DAL) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together during the drive.
Harris (BKN) and Doncic (DAL) briefly engage and disengage as marginal contact occurs off ball.
Durant (BKN) cleanly dislodges the ball from Finney-Smith (DAL) as he defends the driving shot attempt.
Finney-Smith (DAL) is the last player to touch the ball before the ball goes out of bounds.  Possession is correctly awarded to the Nets.
Powell (DAL) maintains verticality and absorbs the contact from Thomas (BKN) during the driving shot attempt.
As Kleber (DAL) and Claxton (BKN) pursue the rebound, incidental arm contact occurs as they attempt to secure the loose ball.
Claxton (BKN) brushes Green's (DAL) arm and marginal contact occurs during rebounding.
Powell (DAL) brushes Thomas' (BKN) arm and marginal contact occurs as Thomas is securing the ball.
Powell (DAL) is moving alongside Thomas' (BKN) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together during the drive.
Brooklyn is awarded a timeout prior to any contact between Doncic (DAL) and O'Neale (BKN) during the drive.
Durant (BKN) lifts and replants his left pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Green (DAL) legally contests Thomas' (BKN) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Durant (BKN) attempts to commit a take foul on Doncic (DAL), and the contact is marginal.
Durant (BKN) commits a take foul on Doncic (DAL).
Kleber (DAL) commits a take foul on Durant (BKN).
Thomas (BKN) commits a take foul on Finney-Smith (DAL).
Durant (BKN) brings his hands towards Kleber (DAL) and marginal contact occurs as Durant releases away.
Durant (BKN) brings his off-arm toward Kleber (DAL) and marginal contact occurs as Durant releases away.
Bullock (DAL) intentionally kicks the ball on the play.
Durant (BKN) brings his arms towards Bullock (DAL) and marginal contact occurs as he releases away.

Bullock (DAL) avoids making contact with Durant (BKN) during his shooting motion.  However, Finney-Smith (DAL) swipes down and makes contact with Durant's arm.  The foul should have been assessed to Finney-Smith.
Powell (DAL) maintains verticality and absorbs contact as he defends O'Neale (BKN) at the end of the drive.
Doncic (DAL) is retreating his arms to a vertical position, and marginal contact with O'Neale's (BKN) right arm occurs as he passes the ball away.
Finney-Smith (DAL) and Harris (BKN) come together at the same spot and marginal contact occurs as Finney-Smith secures the ball.
